From 04a6e11b9376557f7502de695dfe77211cebddb4 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Harish Rachakonda <rachakon@qti.qualcomm.com>
Date: Wed, 25 Jun 2025 22:51:14 +0530
Subject: [PATCH] UPSTREAM:CP ath12k: Add support for new htt_stats 76

Add HTT stats to fetch channel change timings. These stats
are requested from firmware via HTT messages. HTT stats type 76 is
added to collect stats from the firmware. HTT stats type 76 gives
information about overall channel switch time, channel related parameters 
and module wise timings
 
Patch-dependency: None
Patch-work: None

root@OpenWrt:/sys/kernel/debug/ath12k/ahb-c000000.wifi/mac0# echo 76 > htt_stats
_type
root@OpenWrt:/sys/kernel/debug/ath12k/ahb-c000000.wifi/mac0# cat htt_stats

